snippet.title: Cookie Cutter Feature | Feardemic's Fear Fest
snippet.description:
Cookie Cutter is, at its core, a love story between a Companion Denzel -an android powered by a mortal core, and her creator, Doctor Shinji, the greatest engineer of her time. When Shinji is accused of stealing the Red Seed, a powerful fragment of the Void, (a sentient energy source used to power the Megastructure), she is arrested, and Cherry is brutally beaten to pieces. 
This is where her rage (and story) begins...

Wishlist Cookie Cutter on Steam: bit.ly/CookieCutterSteam
